g.title: j1827129097
g.text: How'd you end up joining the Hex, Lettie?

g.title: j1961184476
g.text: But we moved to Libertatia when I was young
You wouldn't know where either place is
Big sprawling place overseas from here

g.title: j3480320374
g.text: Same as most of the others
I was in the ICR with Aoi, Arthur, and Quincy
Everybody needs a medic to glue their ass back together when it gets an extra hole

g.title: j2742426907
g.text: How do you get on with Aoi?

g.title: j4108459158
g.text: I'm surprised you can put up with Quincy. You don't seem to have a lot of patience.

g.title: j2616303087
g.text: Have you found the hole where Arthur keeps the stick he's lodged up there?

g.title: j1835767185
g.text: Where do you call your home

g.title: j4088812294
g.text: Do you have family missing you?

g.title: j3945828072
g.text: Nah, it's the only thing keeping him standing
Man like him is only upright because he's got souls to protect

g.title: j851662151
g.text: Thought it'd be better than working for some mercenary force or army

g.title: j3220254187
g.text: Aoi has to learn when to care for Aoi
Shit, she spends more time babying people than I do Not everybody needs their hand held

g.title: j2663282621
g.text: That boy and his games, I've seen them a thousand times

g.title: j308816086
g.text: I decided a long time ago to follow him to the ends of the earth
And I guess I'm stuck with that choice now, eh

g.title: j3944159845
g.text: Or is the hint in your name?

g.title: j513057393
g.text: Sometimes painful memories are all that get us through.

g.title: j800066475
g.text: We're talking on the *internet* and you know the *phone* exists, yeah?

g.title: j912104272
g.text: She burns herself out that way

g.title: j1887936615
g.text: And knows how to keep his ass out of trouble
That's all I need in a squadmate

g.title: j427381654
g.text: Wasn't the place, it was the person I followed
Arthur's why I'm here and in the ICR in the first place

g.title: j222436253
g.text: This place isn't so bad. Maybe I'll make this my home.

g.title: j696689521
g.text: I make my home wherever I am.

g.title: j914863431
g.text: What do you know of pain?

g.title: j443445598
g.text: Bien podría ser un pinche fantasma
Call from beyond the grave, can't change, can't live, can't die

g.title: j3598899198
g.text: I have to get back to work
Don't have much time for chismes

g.title: j1805540630
g.text: Like shadows on a VHS tape used one too many times

g.title: j4268392240
g.text: Do you know what it feels like to get your head cut off? I do. I've died a thousand times. And it *hurts,* lady.

g.title: j200131339
g.text: No, better they think I am already dead
I take this pain for them

g.title: j2352607390
g.text: Another fantasma like the rest of us
Reliving their deaths again and again and again

g.title: j2493011888
g.text: Do you take the pain for other people by choice, or because it's your duty?

g.title: j192605700
g.text: There's still life worth living, here.

g.title: j4292670861
g.text: The stale popcorn and greasy pizza
Ay, equis, you do you, I won't stop you

g.title: j3880998778
g.text: Yeah, there is family at home
Better they think I am already dead
I will carry this pain for them

g.title: j3080350984
g.text: With Amir's games and Arthur's drinking and Aoi's music and Quincy's pictures

g.title: j3067300884
g.text: Because we're all a bucket of joy
Still, why you don't leave blows my mind

g.title: j2367674780
g.text: Every time I try to stop someone from making stupid decisions it never works
Don't expect it to work now
So I won't waste my time

g.title: j4203128833
g.text: Ten cuidado con lo que deseas
But if that's your flavor, so be it

g.title: j2324001914
g.text: I chose a long time ago
Now it's too late to go back

g.title: j415356728
g.text: Leave Mamá Lettie to her real work
